room_title: Escape room "Curse of the Mayan Temple" by Bust Out Escape Room in Albuquerque
room_address: 7441 Paseo Del Norte Blvd NE Suite G Albuquerque, NM 87113
room_description:
Deep in the Yucatan rain forest lies an ancient Mayan temple believed to be cursed by its last great king named Karbaza. Dr. Carter, the last known explorer to enter the temple, told stories of sacred hidden stones in the vast rain forest and how they could be linked to the curse.
Dr. Carter has not returned from the temple. Now your courageous team has accepted the mission to find Dr. Carter and solve the mystery of the stones. Will your team make it out of the cursed temple alive or will you meet your fate?
